{"tid":1550421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不承認，過去一個月真係輸晒","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:21.000Z","uid":251071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1f708da53d04617cb9f38d5da575b033cfcfd2","tid":1550421,"uid":251071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"呢一個月人地同你打既唔係陣地戰，唔係巷戰，而係<span style=\"color: red;\">心理戰</span><br />\n其實明明我地人多佢咁多，點解次次佢地用十幾人清你幾百人，仲要當你地狗咁打？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實就係輸左係恐懼到</span><br />\n一怕受傷，二怕比人拉有刑責，三怕新屋嶺<br />\n佢就係亂拉亂打再虐待黎製造恐懼嚇怕晒你地<br />\n根本唔洗同你打，未打你地就已經輸左先，人地一衝你地剩係識走<br />\n但其實我地唔係<strong>事實上</strong>會輸，而係<strong>心理上</strong>輸左<br />\n事實就係煙唔驚，子彈唔驚，人仲要多佢好多倍<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最令人恐懼係恐懼本身</span><br />\n唔驚有機會贏，驚就一定輸！"},{"pid":"9dc62746e3e11fb7b610fb6bb52c3d4f28c05f94","tid":1550421,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b22957e4b296254162df45726da62df0d9813334","tid":1550421,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9796ec9d0a7bf7094d84d811beaeb68bddb997b","tid":1550421,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f306d1fbab845c4c624de271a01341c934bd577","tid":1550421,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a0c4c31e92e795363f1a2b150c852cfffe3399","tid":1550421,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}